Package: splineCox
Type: Package
Title: A Two-Stage Estimation Approach to Cox Regression Using M-Spline Function
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Ren Teranishi
Maintainer: Ren Teranishi <ren.teranishi1227@gmail.com>
Description: This package implements a two-stage estimation approach for Cox 
    regression using five-parameter spline functions to model the baseline hazard. It allows 
    for flexible hazard shapes and model selection based on log-likelihood criteria.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
